668
00:44:59,920 --> 00:45:01,480
I miss you too.

669
00:45:02,440 --> 00:45:04,720
We'll get to see
each other often now, right?

670
00:45:05,720 --> 00:45:07,320
We better.

671
00:45:07,600 --> 00:45:09,880
Mi-ran,
I'll be going to the station tomorrow.

672
00:45:10,120 --> 00:45:11,400
See you tomorrow.

673
00:45:11,520 --> 00:45:13,800
Okay, see you tomorrow.

674
00:45:22,160 --> 00:45:25,280
