to make this situation go smoothly, right?

675
00:45:26,040 --> 00:45:27,760
No, you don't have to ask.

676
00:45:27,840 --> 00:45:29,200
All the more reasons to ask.

677
00:45:29,360 --> 00:45:30,440
Is it a man?

678
00:45:31,000 --> 00:45:32,920
-Of course.
-He must be younger than you.

679
00:45:33,440 --> 00:45:34,640
That's right.

680
00:45:35,480 --> 00:45:37,200
-Is he handsome?
-Absolutely.

681
00:45:37,440 --> 00:45:38,920
"Absolutely"?

682
00:45:39,680 --> 00:45:42,280
