694
00:46:18,120 --> 00:46:19,760
Because you like someone else.

695
00:46:24,480 --> 00:46:26,040
You're easily distracted.

696
00:46:26,120 --> 00:46:28,600
How could you like two people
with a single heart?

697
00:46:30,440 --> 00:46:31,600
Wait.

698
00:46:32,120 --> 00:46:35,640
