711
00:47:36,080 --> 00:47:37,320
I know I'm right.

712
00:47:40,200 --> 00:47:41,280
It's Mi-ran.

713
00:47:42,200 --> 00:47:43,600
It's the cryonic man.

714
00:47:44,040 --> 00:47:45,360
That jerk...

715
00:47:45,840 --> 00:47:48,160
