745
00:49:36,400 --> 00:49:39,120
Why would a normal person
without an addiction date her?

746
00:49:39,200 --> 00:49:41,200
Alcoholic Mr. Chu?

747
00:49:41,400 --> 00:49:43,760
Is it a title of a novel
from the Middle Ages?

748
00:49:43,840 --> 00:49:45,640
